{
  "texts": [
    "The prompts we use for finetuning are \"Write a biography for",
    "We take a two-staged approach to learning a reward model.",
    "First, we trained a model to break down a response into individual atomic facts.",
    "Next, we trained a separate model to predict the factuality of each atomic fact.",
    "We then use the predicted factuality of each fact to calculate the overall reward associated with each response."
  ]
}